description: Handcrafted in Aku's Montebelluna, Italy factory the Men's Tribute II GTX pairs a beautiful full grain leather upper with the protection of a Gore-Tex liner to keep your feet dry and comfortable. Match this with an injected polyurethane midsole and a Vibram rubber outsole and the Tribute II GTX will take you on any adventure.
name: Aku Tribute II GTX - Mens

specs.value: Keep your feet dry in all conditions with the integrated waterproof GORE-TEX Performance Comfort membrane
